             was indicted for that <rs id="t17970712-72-off392" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17970712-72-off392" type="offenceCategory" value="deception"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17970712-72-off392" type="offenceSubcategory" value="fraud"></interp>
               she, on the <rs id="t17970712-72-cd393" type="crimeDate">12th of June</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17970712-72-off392 t17970712-72-cd393"></join>, a piece of false and counterfeit money to the likeness of a shilling, unlawfully did utter to 
                     <persName id="t17970712-72-victim766" type="victimName">
                        Edward Isaac 
                        Henman
                     <interp inst="t17970712-72-victim766" type="surname" value="Henman"></interp>
