                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17970712-72-defend765 t17970712-72-punish397"></join>
               Confined six months in Newgate
            </rs>, and find sureties for her good behaviour for six months more.</p>
               <p>Tried by the London Jury, before Mr. COMMON SERJEANT.</p>
